# Pre-commit secret guard — project "персуха" patterns.
# Copy this file to .secretpatterns (gitignored) and fill in REAL values; the
# committed copy must stay generic so it doesn't itself leak anything.
# One extended-regex (grep -E) per line; matched case-insensitively against
# staged additions by .githooks/pre-commit.
#
# Enable the hook once per clone:
#   git config core.hooksPath .githooks
#
# Examples (replace with your own — do NOT commit real values):
# 10\.0\.0\.
# your-internal-host\.example
# YOUR-PC-HOSTNAME
# sk-xxx-
# you@example\.com
